Description_lang: Summons the Eye of Acherus with $s1 health $d that allows vision of nearby area and warns of enemies that attack it.  Right-Click on buff to switch back and forth between Eye of Acherus and normal vision.
AuraDescription_lang: Allows vision through the Eye of Acherus.  Right-Click on buff to switch back and forth between Eye of Acherus and normal vision.
